converts LFQData object to SummarizedExperiment

Source: R/LFQData.R
LFQDataToSummarizedExperiment.Rd

For compatibility with Bioconductor

LFQDataToSummarizedExperiment(lfqdata)

Arguments

lfqdata

LFQData object

Value

SummarizedExperiment (bioconductor)

See also

Other LFQData: LFQDataAggregator, LFQDataPlotter, LFQDataStats, LFQDataSummariser, LFQDataWriter, LFQData, RowAnnotProtein

Examples


istar <- prolfqua_data('data_ionstar')
istar$config <- old2new(istar$config)
data <- istar$data |> dplyr::filter(protein_Id %in% sample(protein_Id, 100))
lfqdata <- LFQData$new(data, istar$config)
lfqdata$to_wide()
